Hi,

I am using apache httpd-2.2.11. It installed and started successfully.
Then I added mod_jk in module and done all the required change. After this when I start apache, It gives following error:


httpd: Syntax error on line 413 of /home/apache/conf/httpd.conf: Syntax error on line 3 of /home/apache/conf/mod-jk.conf: Cannot load /home/apache/modules/mod_jk.so into server: /home/apache/modules/mod_jk.so: ELF file data encoding not little-endian

Please do help me, it is very urgent.

Thanks
~Sangs
You've downloaded an improper binary, try the users mailing list if you're looking for help.
